    "| 5 | **Publish a visualization to the web** | §6 — interactive Leaflet web map deployed via GitHub Pages |\n",
    "| 6 | Web map published via **GitHub Pages** (Lab-09-style) | §6 — `index.html` in the public repo, served at `https://<user>.github.io/<repo>/` |\n",
